com.emc.storageos.model.block

Class NativeContinuousCopyCreate

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.storageos.model.block.NativeContinuousCopyCreate

  • public class NativeContinuousCopyCreate
extends java.lang.Object
    Native continuous copy creation parameters. The name and count values are used to generate volume labels for the mirrors. If count is 1, name is used as the label. If count is greater than 1, name and count are combined to generate labels for the multiple mirrors.
